    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hand tools consisting of a frame with a cutting wheel and drive wheels; used for cutting pipe and tubing by forcing the cutting wheel into the pipe material and rotating the tool around the pipe.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000027101/Smit, Means Illustrated Construction Dictionary (1985)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Handgereedschap dat bestaat uit een frame met een snijwiel en aandrijfwielen. Worden gebruikt om pijpen en buizen te snijden, door het snijwiel in de pijp te duwen en het gereedschap rond de pijp te draaien.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052378/Winkler Prins Encyclopedie (1990)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Handwerkzeug, bestehend aus einem Rahmen mit einem Schneid- und Antriebsrad; wird zum Schneiden von Rohrleitung und Rohr durch das Zwingen des Schneidrades in das Rohrmaterial und Drehen des Werkzeugs um das Rohr verwendet.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>German</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000232/IfM-SMB-PK</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000122134/IfM Berlin</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>架子上裝設有具輪刀與傳動輪所組成的手工具，用於切割管材，方法是藉由將輪刀施力於管材並將工具繞管材旋轉。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
